3
00:00:13,555 --> 00:00:16,349
Could we please stop the <i>90210</i> marathon?

4
00:00:16,433 --> 00:00:18,935
I had a dirty dream
about Andrea Zuckerman.

5
00:00:19,436 --> 00:00:20,895
I'm so confused.

6
00:00:21,479 --> 00:00:24,607
This show is the only thing
getting me through my breakup with Jay.

7
00:00:25,108 --> 00:00:26,776
Oh, I know you're hurting.

8
00:00:26,860 --> 00:00:30,238
But, again, you actually have to date
someone to break up with them.

9
00:00:31,614 --> 00:00:33,658
[Leia scoffs] I like it better under here.

10
00:00:33,742 --> 00:00:37,579
Oh my God. Still with the <i>90210?</i>
This is getting pathetic.

11
00:00:37,662 --> 00:00:40,915
I'm not gonna say it to her face,
but she needs professional help.

12
00:00:41,458 --> 00:00:43,710
I saw her yesterday wandering
just through the neighborhood

13
00:00:43,793 --> 00:00:45,420
like our grandpa used to.

14
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:46,838
Near the end.

15
00:00:48,423 --> 00:00:49,924
Guys, stop.

16
00:00:50,008 --> 00:00:51,634
She's going through something.

17
00:00:51,718 --> 00:00:53,887
Something really stupid.

18
00:00:55,055 --> 00:00:56,264
Gwen! I'm right here!

19
00:00:56,765 --> 00:00:58,224
Good. You needed to hear it.

20
00:00:58,308 --> 00:00:59,476
[scoffs]

21
00:00:59,559 --> 00:01:01,519
