22
00:01:01,603 --> 00:01:04,856
It takes about half the time
you were in a relationship to get over it.

23
00:01:04,939 --> 00:01:07,609
And since you were never
<i>in</i> a relationship…

24
00:01:08,818 --> 00:01:09,819
You're good.

25
00:01:09,903 --> 00:01:10,945
[Leia scoffs]

26
00:01:11,029 --> 00:01:13,990
Leia, come on.
Don't go back into your sad hole.

27
00:01:14,074 --> 00:01:16,493
We came by to give you
your birthday present.

28
00:01:16,576 --> 00:01:18,203
