-[Bob laughs]

84
00:03:48,394 --> 00:03:49,938
[Kitty coos]

85
00:03:50,021 --> 00:03:50,939
You knew about this?

86
00:03:51,022 --> 00:03:53,066
And you didn't, and that's why he's here.

87
00:03:53,149 --> 00:03:54,776
-Hi!
-[Bob] Hi.

88
00:03:54,859 --> 00:03:57,820
I brought you some fresh Florida oranges.

89
00:03:57,904 --> 00:03:59,989
