for the party.

164
00:07:44,714 --> 00:07:47,842
Oh, that's sweet,
but we have plenty of food for tonight.

165
00:07:47,925 --> 00:07:50,720
I know, but the kids are gonna want
something good.

166
00:07:52,513 --> 00:07:54,891
I was thawing a ham in there.

167
00:07:56,267 --> 00:07:58,019
I'm just excited.

168
00:07:58,102 --> 00:08:02,231
You know, I went all out
on Leia's birthday gift this year.

169
00:08:02,315 --> 00:08:04,609
