170
00:08:05,610 --> 00:08:08,821
-Aren't those things expensive?
-Oh yeah. [chuckles]

171
00:08:08,905 --> 00:08:10,531
I left the price tag on.

172
00:08:11,991 --> 00:08:13,910
'Cause I want her to…

173
00:08:13,993 --> 00:08:15,995
